		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Beats Dr. Wily in some kind of parallel universe
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Aims for fastest time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Manipulates luck
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Takes damage to save time
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"This run improves upon the 
	[a class=intlink href=/4926S 
		"published movie
	]a
	" by 1013 frames, or 
	(frames|amount=1013|fps=59.727500569606)
	" seconds, mostly by improved RNG and strategy changes.
	$LF
